<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.2">
<l>kāṇṭā vaṉameṉ patorkā ṭamarark karaiya ṉatukaṇ ṭavaṉniṟ kamuṉē</l>
<l>mūṇṭā raḻaluṇ ṇamuṉin tatuvu matuvaṉ ṟiyummuṉ ṉulakam poṟaitīrt</l>
<l>tāṇṭā ṉavuṇa ṉavaṉmār vakala mukirāl vakirā kamuṉin tariyāy</l>
<l>nīṇṭāṉ kuṟaḷā kinimirn tavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for the one who stretched [tall] as a dwarf,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who extended [out] as a lion</l>
<l>Raging, so that the demon’s broad chest became lumps [of flesh]</l>
<l rend="indent">because of his claws,</l>
<l>The one who, aside from being enraged so that a spreading fire, burning,</l>
<l rend="indent">also consumed the forest called Khāṇḍava,</l>
<l rend="indent">in front the king of the immortals as he stood watching it,</l>
<l>Long ago ruled the earth having removed [its] burden,</l>
<l rend="indent">is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
